Package com.sri.ai.util.rangeoperation.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AggregateOperator<V,R>
    Represents an aggregate operator by defining initializing and incrementing functions.
    DAEFunction
    An object that computes a value from a DependencyAwareEnvironment.
    DependencyAwareEnvironment
    An extension of Map that is able to keep track and manage dependencies between its entries as computed by DAEFunctions.
    Range<T>
    A range can be thought of as a "virtual list" of values for a named variable, based on a generator of values or an actual collection.
    RangeOperation<T1,T2>
    A combination of AggregateOperator and Range.
